KQL query to find amount of data stored in tables
Usage
| where TimeGenerated > startofday(ago(31d))
| where StartTime > startofday(ago(31d))
| where IsBillable == true
| summarize TotalVolumeGB = sum(Quantity) / 1024 by DataType
| render columnchart

Query for daily ingestion 
Usage
| where TimeGenerated > ago(7d)
| where IsBillable == true
| extend Timing = format_datetime(TimeGenerated,"dd-MM-yy")
| summarize TotalVolumeGB = sum(Quantity) / 1024 by DataType , Timing
| where DataType has "AzureDiagnostics"
| order by TotalVolumeGB desc 


Query for Monthly ingestion
Usage
| where TimeGenerated > ago(30d)
| where IsBillable == true
| summarize TotalVolumeGB = sum(Quantity) / 1024
| order by TotalVolumeGB desc 


