Get ingestion volume in Container Log by Container Id -
let startdatetime = "yyyy-mm-dd";
let enddatetime = "yyyy-mm-dd";
ContainerLog
| where TimeGenerated  between (todatetime(startdatetime) .. todatetime(enddatetime))
| extend Timing = format_datetime(TimeGenerated,"MM-yyyy") 
| summarize sum(_BilledSize) by ContainerID,Computer,Timing
| project TotalVolume=format_bytes(sum__BilledSize,0,"GB"),ContainerID,Computer,Timing
| where TotalVolume != "0 GB"
| distinct ContainerID;


Get list of Pods against container ids found in above query list - 
