AMA Agent enable disable on AKS cluster
Below steps were followed to fix the issue à
	1) Disable Azure monitor agent via Az cli : az aks disable-addons --resource-group <rg_name> --name <cluster_name> --addons monitoring
	2) Wait for 5-10 minutes
	3) Re enable the Azure Monitor agent via Az cli : az aks enable-addons --resource-group <rg_name> --name <cluster_name>--addons monitoring --workspace-resource-id ""

